        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\n> Patch Set 3: Verified+1 Code-Review+2\n> \n> Just a note, when this container version is released/updated into OOM, we also need to update the port on testsuite repo - https://gerrit.onap.org/r/gitweb?p=testsuite.git;a=blob;f=robot/resources/dcae_interface.robot;h=7b1b4b2480316a9c66c2a79a95d92a87032c61e6;hb=HEAD\n> GLOBAL_DCAE_HEALTH_SERVER_PORT should be set to 8080\n\nNo, there's no change needed.   The dcae-healthcheck service still responds on port 80.  The OOM charts for healthcheck need to change to make sure that the service maps back to port 8080 on the container.",
